                        <div id="page-title">
                            Highest Rated SCPs
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<p>These are the highest rated SCPs on the site, listed with creation date and who posted the page. Note that articles posted in July '08 were by and large brought over from the previous site, and so the page creator will often not be the author of the article.</p>
<p>If an SCP is not listed here but should be, then it doesn't have the &quot;scp&quot; tag.</p>
<hr />
<div class="list-pages-box">    

